Subject: URGENT! FPL- Wrong item sent for PO 8538XK. Case Number: 11619820
BodyText:
This email originated outside of TD SYNNEX.  Please help keep our organization and partners safe. It's up to us; think before you click.

Good morning, team:

This email relates to PO 8538XK. The customer informed us that he received the wrong item.

PO 8538XK was submitted for a "LOGITECH BRIO 90 FPS USB TYPE A WEBCAM"; unfortunately, instead of this item, the customer received "a type B usb for a printer".

I would appreciate your help, as the customer is asking how he can return the wrong product to receive the correct one.

Thanks in advance for your support.

Best.
Bedsaida
CC55
